How to Download Mongo DB
1.	Go onto your browser and clink on this link: Try MongoDB Products | MongoDB.
2.	Choose which type of deployment: On-premises MongoDB locally and then choose the MongoDB Community Server.
 

3.	Go to your downloads folder and double click on the .msi package.
 

4.	Click the Next button to start installation

 


5.	Check the Accept License Agreement and then select the Next button.
 

6.	Select Complete 
  




7.	Select Run service as Network Service user‚Äù and note the directory for later use.
  

8.	Deselect MongoDB compass then click Next, because you can select install MongoDB Compass if it is required.
 


9.	Click on the Install to begin installation.
  

10.	Click Finish to complete the installation.
 
